{
  "texts": [
    "These features serve as a specification of different levels of compliance of a catalogue against the related dimension and provide a categorical view to assess the maturity of catalogues of semantic artefacts.",
    "The target audience of our work and the maturity model presented here refers to at least the following users:",
    "• Semantic artefact providers may benefit from the model by understanding the criteria that make their artefacts more discoverable and usable.",
    "• Users of semantic artefacts can leverage the maturity model to assess and compare different catalogues, gaining insights into the reliability and relevance of the offered artefacts.",
    "Both providers and users can rely on the model to select catalogues that align with their specific needs and expectations, e.g."
  ]
}